# 数据存储模块 Skills

## 模块概述
数据存储模块使用 IndexedDB (Dexie.js) 实现本地数据持久化，支持响应式查询。

## 核心文件
- `src/app/db/db.ts` - 数据库定义
- `src/app/utils/storage.ts` - 存储层API
- `src/app/store/useConfigStore.ts` - 配置状态管理

## 数据库结构

```typescript
// 位置: src/app/db/db.ts
class AppDatabase extends Dexie {
  projects!: Table<Project>;
  chapters!: Table<Chapter>;
  scripts!: Table<Script>;
  storyboards!: Table<Storyboard>;
  assets!: Table<AssetLibrary>;
  templates!: Table<StoryboardTemplate>;
  versions!: Table<ProjectVersion>;
  relations!: Table<CharacterRelation>;

  constructor() {
    super('AIComicStudioDB');
    this.version(1).stores({
      projects: 'id',
      chapters: 'id, projectId',
      scripts: 'id, chapterId',
      storyboards: 'id, chapterId',
      assets: 'projectId',
      templates: 'id',
      versions: 'id, projectId',
      relations: 'id, projectId'
    });
  }
}
```

